{"tid":1916612,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"北美/ 美國股票MPF 既巴絲入黎注意下","createTime":"2020-03-09T03:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T13:00:01.000Z","uid":3241,"like":8,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"3545222b88159140d6c2ebb7b8472c940a8d6074","tid":1916612,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:29:21.000Z","msg":"繼上次苦口婆心叫人唔好用宏利後，今天要講下就係支那武肺搞到環球股市大跌MPF 點做好<br />\n<br />\n首先我地用一隻特別ETF，18年美國隊長都介紹過既PTLC<br />\n<br />\n1. 呢隻ETF係SP500指數係200日平均線以上就會all-in sp500<br />\n2. 當有連續5個交易日低於200天平均線就會改為一半sp500，一半係短期國債<br />\n3. 當後5個交易日繼續係低於200天線，就連剩低果半都轉為國債<br />\n4. 當低谷過後，有連續5個連續交易日指數上番200天線以上，就會再一次all-in sp500，唔會再轉一半先。<br />\n<br />\n講完廢話，大家撳一撳條LINK睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.paceretfs.com/media/trendpilot_tracker.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paceretfs.com%2Fmedia%2Ftrendpilot_tracker.pdf&d=rROtLXfiIyO0AijGL7caM9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=3534f111\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.paceretfs.com/media/trendpilot_tracker.pdf</a><br />\n如果大家覺得呢一浪係會KEEP住仆街落去，唔似上年年尾2個月唔夠就反彈既，數據就話你聽應該準備轉去防守方向了，當然新供款梗係繼續買美股襯低入貨，但現有資產都應該做少少防禦動作"},{"pid":"fcb5d7757c5d5e091b1f57ba24a1a7700c071d27","tid":1916612,"uid":232817,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:36:13.000Z","msg":"宏利真係痴撚線，升得少過人跌得多過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df5957bea38fe24d0858031b367abc79e1b2379","tid":1916612,"uid":60155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:36:30.000Z","msg":"唔明"},{"pid":"70ab20f78d05f9c5339153ed37d4e7771da4e541","tid":1916612,"uid":255980,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fcb5d7757c5d5e091b1f57ba24a1a7700c071d27","tid":1916612,"uid":232817,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:36:13.000Z","msg":"宏利真係痴撚線，升得少過人跌得多過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:38:26.000Z","msg":"跌左十分一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c084b338eba2295cf4a32c83266ae8f4492af5a3","tid":1916612,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7df5957bea38fe24d0858031b367abc79e1b2379","tid":1916612,"uid":60155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:36:30.000Z","msg":"唔明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:40:50.000Z","msg":"簡單d 講，當你怕美股會一炮蒸發左你十幾年嘅供款， 你就應該係指數踩入200天簡單移動平均線以下個區域就做防守部署<br />\n<br />\n當然， 如果好似18年尾果下， 你轉左唔夠一個月就急升返曬， 你係會有損失。"},{"pid":"8e0b1c09f3fbfb855a817258c0cd6482a74da484","tid":1916612,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:46:12.000Z","msg":"依家邊間mpf抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65aed8559036566fb275179d88bbf01fff072b2c","tid":1916612,"uid":133501,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T04:05:09.000Z","msg":"MPF股神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"124b141edbca61c89ae4db41334c5e19d95a803d","tid":1916612,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8e0b1c09f3fbfb855a817258c0cd6482a74da484","tid":1916612,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:46:12.000Z","msg":"依家邊間mpf抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T04:12:42.000Z","msg":"跌市梗係揀管理費低既基金<br />\n做防守部署都係65歲懶人或者債卷<br />\n所謂保證基金真係食屎來的，收2%管理費，你一年利息都冇咁多，點會有回報"},{"pid":"328d67705a08d3499e2482d5de76945b9a34e67b","tid":1916612,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T04:14:57.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"cce56411f47e78c8a42e36ca93e653af1af7817b","tid":1916612,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T04:15:21.000Z","msg":"gg 上年6月先轉宏利因為個FD 係入面做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91cad877b1ecfce2fd7ad89c4672e1f5a6852bd8","tid":1916612,"uid":64787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite